room_title: Escape room "Eddy's Organs" by Escape House in Rexburg
room_description:
Eddy is a virtuoso on the Organ. He can make the notes on the page come alive in a cacophony of symphonic harmony similar to Bach himself. However, Eddy doesn't always make the best decisions. His latest decision with his health on the line has left him in dire need.
You receive a communication from his doctor explaining what needs to be done. You are Eddy's only hope. Will you get to it in time, or has Eddy already played his last fugue?
